--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This is a module that is designed to perform the following tasks:

-- Read the /proc/stat continuously on a regular basis.

-- Calculate the percentage from the below sets of values that we have populated:
    * User time            * IO-wait time
    * Nice time            * IRQ time
    * System time          * Soft-IRQ time
    * Idle time            * Steal time
    * Guest time           * Guest nice time

-- Display the received percentage in terms of a Gertboard based LED sets.
-- Facilitates the user to change the /proc/stat read interval via Gertboard
   switches.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
